	Merge branch 'canned_bootstrap'

	first crack at a pre-built bootstrap setup where "bootstrap" (everything generated by said target) is archived and can be published -- a file using the Makefile lines for all of the bootstrap targets and package versions is created and checksum'd... we then use that checksum to determine if we can fetch/extract a pre-built bootstrap tarball, or if we need to build fresh

