	Merge branch '306_updates' into 3.x.x

	install.sh: when performing an in-place upgrade, sometimes kpartx/losetup fail to cleanup the loop device properly when the image package is used from some other file system / medium (eg, NFS) -- handle this by performing a sync first, and then if either program fails, wait a few seconds then try it again before failing permanently

